Chhota Bheem (transl.â€‰Little Bheem) is an Indian animated comedy adventure television
 series, created by Green Gold Animations based in Hyderabad.
  This show is available in English, Hindi, Telugu,Tamil, Kannada, Malayalam and Marathi. 
  Bheem is a brave, strong and intelligent young boy. 
  He often manages to solve everyone's problems which endears him to the townspeople of Dholakpur.[1]

